---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Menu from '../components/Menu.vue';
---

<Layout title="About - Notes by Hash Milhan" description="Hi. I'm Hash—short for Hashir. I am a Senior Creative Director & Technologist at Publicis Groupe MENA in Dubai.">
	<Header />
	
	<main class="container py-12">
		<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
			<!-- Two-column layout -->
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
				<!-- Left column - Heading -->
				<div class="lg:col-span-4">
					<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-primary text-white leading-tight sticky top-24">
						About Hash Milhan
					</h1>
				</div>
				
				<!-- Right column - Content -->
				<div class="lg:col-span-8">
					<article class="prose-minimal">
						<div class="space-y-6 text-lg font-text leading-relaxed">
							<p class="text-text-light">
								Hi. I'm <em>Hash</em>—short for Hashir. I am a <strong class="text-white">Senior Creative Director & Technologist</strong> at <strong class="text-white">Publicis Groupe MENA</strong> in Dubai.
							</p>
							
							<p class="text-text-light">
								I've been working in the creative industry for over a decade, specializing in the intersection of creativity and technology. My work spans <strong class="text-white">AI-driven creative projects</strong>, <strong class="text-white">web development</strong>, and <strong class="text-white">digital innovation</strong>.
							</p>
							
							<p class="text-text-light">
								I enjoy playing with web technologies, Gen AI, social AR platforms, UX, voice tech, IoT/smart devices and cryptocurrencies—whenever I can understand what's going on!
							</p>
							
							<p class="text-text-light">
								This blog is where I share my thoughts on emerging technologies, creative processes, and the future of digital experiences. From AI-generated art to cutting-edge web frameworks, I explore how technology can amplify human creativity.
							</p>
							
							<p class="text-text-light">
								A lot of my free time is also spent on watching movies and TV shows—mostly in the comic book genre, which is fuelled by my collection of Marvel, DC and Image comics in long boxes collecting dust.
							</p>
							
							<p class="text-text-light">
								I also have a collection of various cameras from different time periods. These range from film cameras to my most recent acquisition of the Canon 6D DSLR, which I use for most of my photography now (along with my iPhone 12 Pro Max).
							</p>
						</div>
						
						<!-- Social Links Section -->
						<div class="mt-16 pt-8">
							<h2 class="text-2xl font-primary text-white mb-8">You can find me on:</h2>
							
